	h2 So what concrete changes might this philosophy create?

	p
		| It's obviously impossible to predict the future, but here are some of the things we believe Crowdsell makes possible in the world. We think the changes could be massive, and we invite you to use your imagination about what this could bring, and we're sure we haven't thought of everything. And some of these things might not happen, but we're going to actively work to
		i make them happen
